{"type":"object","properties":{"MIMEType":{"title":"Attachment mime type","type":"string"},"ID":{"title":"Attachment ID","type":"string"},"Name":{"title":"Attachment name","type":"string"},"Size":{"title":"Attachment size","type":"integer"}}},"BCC[*]":{"type":"object","properties":{"Name":{"title":"Bcc name","type":"string"},"Email":{"title":"Bcc email","type":"string"}}},"CC[*]":{"type":"object","properties":{"Email":{"title":"Cc","type":"string"},"Name":{"title":"Cc name","type":"string"}}},"Categories[*]":{"type":"object","properties":{"ID":{"title":"Category ID","type":"string"},"Name":{"title":"Category name","type":"string"}}},"To[*]":{"type":"object","properties":{"Email":{"title":"To","type":"string"},"Name":{"title":"Recipient name","type":"string"}}},"From":{"type":"object","properties":{"Email":{"title":"From","type":"string"},"Name":{"title":"Sender name","type":"string"}}},"ParentFolders[*]":{"type":"object","properties":{"ID":{"title":"Email folder or label","type":"string"},"Name":{"title":"Label","type":"string"}}}}}},"telemetryData":{"operation":"EMAIL_RECEIVED","objectName":"Message","connectorKey":"uipath-google-gmail","connectorName":"Gmail","primaryKeyName":""},"inputMetadata":{},"errorState":{"hasError":false},"bindings":[{"resource":"Property","key":"EMAIL_RECEIVED","value":{"ParentFolders[*].ID":{"defaultValue":"INBOX","isExpression":false}},"metadata":{"TriggerCreateParameters":"ParentFolders[*].ID","DebugQueryParameters":"ParentFolders[*].ID","BindingsVersion":"2.2","ObjectName":"Message"}}]}]]></uipath:input>
